      • fillUseProfile

        private void fillUseProfile(int activity)
        This method reads the probabilities for the appliance to be used at a specific time from the activity statistics file. Each double array contains either the weekday or the weekend probabilities for all time intervals for a specific active occupancy. Therefore, the list will contain six double arrays.
